        <div class="a24" style="padding-bottom: 10PX;"> 
         <h1 class="a25"> 2017年鹤壁职业技术学院高职单招简章</h1> 
         <p> <span class="a42"> 2017/3/22 14:02:52 标签：<a href="/tags_%e9%b9%a4%e5%a3%81%e8%81%8c%e4%b8%9a%e6%8a%80%e6%9c%af%e5%ad%a6%e9%99%a2.html" target="_blank" class="a40">鹤壁职业技术学院</a> &nbsp;<a href="/tags_%e9%ab%98%e8%81%8c%e5%8d%95%e6%8b%9b.html" target="_blank" class="a40">高职单招</a> &nbsp;<a href="/tags_%e6%8b%9b%e7%94%9f%e7%ae%80%e7%ab%a0.html" target="_blank" class="a40">招生简章</a> &nbsp;</span> </p> 
         <span style="float: right;"> 
          <div id="bdshare" class="bdshare_t bds_tools get-codes-bdshare"> 
